      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark problems including cantilever beam and Hertzian contact were solved and compared to analytical solutions; errors were within 0.5%, confirming code correctness at the required gradation."
    },
