      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "A systematic mesh convergence study was performed across three refinement levels. The reported quantity of interest (peak von Mises stress at screw-rod junction) changed by less than 2% between the medium and fine meshes, satisfying Gradation 3 criteria."
    },
