      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Model setup was independently reviewed by a second analyst. Boundary conditions, material assignments, and contact definitions were verified against the documented simulation plan prior to execution."
