      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic constitutive models were applied to titanium alloy components. Literature and prior validation studies support this choice for the sub-yield loading regime of the F1717 test. Simplifying assumptions (e.g., bonded screw-rod interface) were documented and their impact assessed via sensitivity analysis."
    },
    {
