      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Measured specimen dimensions and material properties from physical testing were used directly as FEA inputs, ensuring high fidelity between the simulation and experimental configurations. Discrepancies were quantified and found to be within measurement uncertainty."
    },
    {
