      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "FEA-predicted construct stiffness and peak load at yield were compared against experimental measurements using both graphical overlays and quantitative metrics (RMSE, percent error). Mean percent error was 4.2%, within the pre-specified 10% acceptance threshold."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
